PrecisAppointment of RONALD LAYDEN of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Foundation for Innovation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Michel Kelly-Gagnon, whose term has expired.
